From the following JSON, extract only the value of the "name" field (the new colleague's full name). Output just the name as plain text.

JSON:
{
  "name": "Dora",
  "email": null,
  "channels": [
    "general",
    "random"
  ]
}

From the following JSON, extract only the value of the "email" field (the new colleague's email address). Output just the email as plain text.

JSON:
{
  "name": "Dora",
  "email": null,
  "channels": [
    "general",
    "random"
  ]
}
